{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                                // hydrogen // schema // audio"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Audio pillar (Pillar 10b) - synthesis, processing, analysis, and voice."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Leader module documenting all audio sub-modules."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Core Audio"},{"LineComment":" | - **Level**: Amplitude atoms (Decibel, LinearGain, dBFS)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Frequency**: Pitch atoms (Hertz, MidiNote, Cent, Semitone, Octave)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Time**: Temporal atoms (BeatTime, BarTime, SampleCount)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Spatial**: Stereo/3D positioning (Pan, Balance, Azimuth, Elevation)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Synthesis"},{"LineComment":" | - **Synthesis**: Filter/oscillator params (Cutoff, Resonance, Drive)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Oscillator**: Waveform types and configuration"},{"LineComment":" | - **Envelope**: ADSR atoms (Attack, Decay, Sustain, Release)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Filter**: Filter types and configurations"},{"LineComment":" | - **Modulation**: LFO params (ModDepth, ModRate, LFOPhase)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Effects"},{"LineComment":" | - **Effects**: Reverb, Delay, Compressor, EQ, Distortion, Gate, Limiter"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Analysis"},{"LineComment":" | - **Analysis**: Metering atoms (RMS, Peak, FFT)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Voice & Speech"},{"LineComment":" | - **Voice**: Voice synthesis atoms (pitch, rate, breathiness, expression)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Formant**: Vocal tract modeling (F1-F5, vowel shapes, vocoder)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Speech**: Speech recognition output (phonemes, words, speakers)"},{"LineComment":" | - **VoiceCompounds**: Higher-level voice compositions (VoiceCharacter, Dialogue)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Accessibility"},{"LineComment":" | - **Accessibility**: Screen readers, audio descriptions, sonification, earcons"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Triggers"},{"LineComment":" | - **Trigger**: Event-based audio playback for UI feedback"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" | Audio primitives model synthesis concepts, not Web Audio API methods."},{"LineComment":" | Voice primitives describe WHAT a voice sounds like, not specific TTS APIs."},{"LineComment":" | Conversion to Web Audio, MIDI, or other backends happens at boundaries."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Agent Voice at Billion-Scale"},{"LineComment":" | These primitives enable deterministic voice synthesis:"},{"LineComment":" | - Same VoiceCharacter = same voice identity across all agents"},{"LineComment":" | - Emotional shifts modify voice without losing identity"},{"LineComment":" | - Multi-turn dialogues with speaker attribution"},{"LineComment":" | - Accessibility-first design for inclusive interfaces"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Level as Level"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Frequency as Freq"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Voice as Voice"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.VoiceCompounds as VC"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Define an agent voice"},{"LineComment":" | agentVoice = VC.voiceCharacter"},{"LineComment":" |   \"Assistant\""},{"LineComment":" |   VC.PersonaFriendly"},{"LineComment":" |   Voice.voiceProfileDefault"},{"LineComment":" |   (Formant.formantSetFromVowel Formant.VowelSchwa)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Apply emotional shift"},{"LineComment":" | excitedVoice = VC.applyShiftToCharacter"},{"LineComment":" |   (VC.emotionalShift Voice.expressionJoyful 1.2 VC.TransitionSmooth)"},{"LineComment":" |   agentVoice"},{"LineComment":" | ```"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,35],"start":[72,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio.purs","reExports":{},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,35],"start":[72,1]}}